{"tid":1248384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察依家連自己總部比人圍 都唔敢清 做警察既人有冇好好反省自己？","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T15:33:42.000Z","uid":42246,"like":387,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"914642fe7ba3c2dc191f1cb49acd5fdb31a2dc3e","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"首先咪再以為你地自己係正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係3萬人正義&gt;200萬人正義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係正義你呀頭 一哥咁樣比人圍總部 落曬面<br />\n搞到依家重唔清？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日示威者擋路 市民鬧既係政府同警察 唔係示威者（cctvb播）<br />\n<br />\n你地係公仆來 政府都應該係為市民服務<br />\n（特首都走出來認衰）<br />\n<br />\n依家搞到 政府代表中共 你地代表政府<br />\n簡單講 做狗隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心你啦 過街老鼠黑警 你重以正義自稱 但連自己號碼都唔敢比人睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全社會睇你地唔起 係你地自己拎來<br />\n當真正正義係面前 你地選擇屈服上頭命令<br />\n（講你地都係打扮工？ 我地市民唔洗打？ 一樣照罷工）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你同我講自己係英雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a2cc725178a2d6e5e78f8d8fe2ecda0afcc1db","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2edfcbb3839068cad9faf3d088d8b5057b40c6c8","tid":1248384,"uid":247905,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"黑警全部都係食屎狗"},{"pid":"f459e92e7e45550ad569a445be0c765c535ca98d","tid":1248384,"uid":13117,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"老實，搞到咁都仲唔反省下，係人唔係？"},{"pid":"08ddf9f3214e7438378272a6e96a9712da188d49","tid":1248384,"uid":156623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"全民排斥黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b738999e42ca5437596c11c7d15a9237cee476da","tid":1248384,"uid":98431,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"認清目標 聚焦醫警濫權<br />\n<br />\n修例係撤回定停止已經唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n今日圍完 應該盡早散 僵持不下無意思<br />\n<br />\n國際人權組織已經出左報告 今晚有意外就前功盡廢了<br />\n<br />\n手足辛苦完 應該到宣傳組出場<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位耐心睇完"},{"pid":"b741811ae581fb76245ca7e931e5809979720d1e","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"08ddf9f3214e7438378272a6e96a9712da188d49","tid":1248384,"uid":156623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"全民排斥黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"真心要 所有鋪頭應該杯佢地<br />\n等佢地唔敢抬頭出街<br />\n唔敢同人講自己係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恰佢地小朋友 就大家睇自己<br />\n我重有少少道德高地所以唔會<br />\n但其他人做我都體諒"},{"pid":"3810b288b71952ca6b8db27d085e50c4766de790","tid":1248384,"uid":25080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"d12d78545ca8519495d82f051e777f266781f9af","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b738999e42ca5437596c11c7d15a9237cee476da","tid":124