\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係3萬人正義&gt;200萬人正義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係正義你呀頭 一哥咁樣比人圍總部 落曬面<br />\n搞到依家重唔清？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日示威者擋路 市民鬧既係政府同警察 唔係示威者（cctvb播）<br />\n<br />\n你地係公仆來 政府都應該係為市民服務<br />\n（特首都走出來認衰）<br />\n<br />\n依家搞到 政府代表中共 你地代表政府<br />\n簡單講 做狗隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心你啦 過街老鼠黑警 你重以正義自稱 但連自己號碼都唔敢比人睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全社會睇你地唔起 係你地自己拎來<br />\n當真正正義係面前 你地選擇屈服上頭命令<br />\n（講你地都係打扮工？ 我地市民唔洗打？ 一樣照罷工）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你同我講自己係英雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"無錯，誰大誰惡誰正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b57e9a9e31504f44a4d11b92148e933701b7afa","tid":1248384,"uid":245803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"唔係唔清，係搞小動作啫"},{"pid":"9c55a1e34a96a659060adea2d58b2cdf30d6a849","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfb919fea0335578433fa935e944ccc3861fb4e","tid":1248384,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"香港最低賤人種：<br />\n清潔工<br />\n警察<br />\n地盤工人"},{"pid":"8ceb354745b6434d22e6de8bafa9237d1cdbfb73","tid":1248384,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cfb919fe